G.description:
The blob that refers to the price entry data that was previously uploaded to a Blob in EVA. If left empty the inline data will be used.

The data in the blob must be in the following format:

[
    {
      "ProductID": "<ProductID>",
      "Price": <Price>
    },
    ...
]
